# Design system

This app uses plain CSS with design tokens. There is no Tailwind and no SF Pro.

## Tokens

- All tokens live in `src/styles/tokens.css` as CSS custom properties.
- Color, surface, ink, border, and accent values come from those variables. Do not introduce one-off hex values where a token exists.
- Spacing uses the `--space-*` scale. Radius uses the `--radius-*` scale.

## Type

Two tiers, both self-hosted via Fontsource:

- Body: Geist Medium, 14 / 20, via `--font-body` and `--font-sans`.
- Display: Inter, 20 / 28, via `--font-display` (name, leads, case titles).

## Styling

- Global styles are split across `src/styles/tokens.css`, `base.css`, and `app.css`. Exploration demos add `exploration-preview.css`.
- Match the existing class naming (for example the `cs__*` case-study classes). Prefer extending existing patterns over new one-offs.

## Motion

- Animation uses Motion and GSAP. Honor `prefers-reduced-motion`: motion and the animated grain freeze, and entrance transitions collapse to instant.
- Keep durations and easing consistent with the `MotionConfig` defaults in `src/main.jsx`.
